Format: ICO (Windows Icon)
Dimensions: Multiple sizes included in single file
- 16x16 pixels (browser tabs, bookmarks)
- 32x32 pixels (taskbar, dock, retina displays)
- 48x48 pixels (desktop shortcuts, high-DPI displays)

Colors:
- Primary: #2563EB (Brand blue)
- Background: #FFFFFF (White)
- Color depth: 32-bit with alpha channel

Design:
- Simple, recognizable icon representing the AI-SMS Lead Platform
- High contrast ratio (4.5:1 minimum) for accessibility
- Clean edges for small size legibility
- Transparent background support
- Optimized for both light and dark mode visibility

File Requirements:
- Maximum file size: 10KB
- Lossless compression
- Multiple resolution support
- Alpha channel transparency

Cache Control Headers:
Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable

The icon should be created using professional icon design software (like Adobe Illustrator or Sketch) 
and exported using an ICO converter tool that supports multiple resolutions in a single file.